title: Avengers-Defenders War - 1973 Marvel Crossover
description: Loki and Dormammu conspire against the Avengers and Defenders and pit them against each other. Powerful pawns in a game of gods! Captain America vs. the Submariner! Thor vs. the Hulk! The Swordsman vs. the Valkyrie! These and other matches comprised the Silver Age's most sensational clash of costumed champions, but whoever wins the war, Dormammu and Loki are prepared to make Earth the loser!
